## Naming conventions in code

| Concept | Variable/type name | Example value |
|---------|-------------------|---------------|
| Our project ID | `appProjectId` | `"proj_abc123"` |
| v0 project ID | `v0ProjectId` | `"prj_xyz"` |
| v0 chat ID | `v0ChatId` / `chatId` | `"chat_abc"` |
| Preview URL | `demoUrl` / `currentDemoUrl` | `"https://v0-abc.vusercontent.net"` |
| Deployed URL | `url` (in deployment) | `"https://my-site.vercel.app"` |
| Entry mode | `buildMethod` | `"wizard"` |
| Build type | `buildIntent` | `"website"` |
